The successes and failures of businesses near the former World Trade Center site can be traced to multiple factors.
<P>


<font  face="times new roman"><b><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2002/02/03/politics/03REBU.html?todaysheadlines">Bush Administration Approves $700 Million Grant to Help Rebuild Lower Manhattan</a></b><br>
